[[Afaylu:Zahor lhcen - lḥsn zzahur.png|vignette|Amara d umdyaz amrruki " Lḥsn Zahur"]]Iga '''Lḥsn Zahur''' (الحسن زهور, lahcen zaheur) amara d unfran amrruki, ilul g [[Imi n Ugadir|Imi n ugadir]] ɣ usggʷas 1958. 

Yumẓ taslkint tamsdawt (licence) n irzzutn g taskla taɛṛabt, ɣ tasdawit n tskla d tmassanin tanafganin, Lqaḍi Ɛyyaḍ g [[Mrrakc|Mṛṛakc]], asggʷas n 1983.

Ig amslay g umaris n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt.

== Idlisn n umara ==

* ́Adlis n « Muzya » d iffɣn g usggʷas n 1994, tasiggzt ‘ssalam’ agadir. lli ismann kigan n taddminin timaziɣin.
* Tullisin « Amussu n umalu » asufɣ n usggʷas n 2008, g tasiggzt  ‘alqalam’, g ugadir.
* Tullisin « Isggʷasn n tgrst » asufɣ n usggʷas n 2009,  g tasiggzt ‘alqalam’ agadir.
* Adlis « Ɛica mmu yiɣd » asggʷas n 2010, d issufɣ usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt.
* Adlis « Aṛṣmiḍ » assuɣl n tawuri n ‘nikulay gugul’ asggʷas 2012.
* Tullisin « Tayri d iẓilliḍ », asggʷas n 2014. g tasiggzt n ‘dar assalam’ ɣ ṛṛbaṭ, gant zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, d tamdrawt d tmawast n tussna tamṛṛukit.
* Adlis n « Umiyn d umiyn n Ayt Ndi » asggʷas n 2016, g tasiggzt n ‘dar assalam’ ɣ ṛṛbaṭ, iga zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, d tamdrawt d tmawast n tussna tamṛṛukit.
* Tullisin « Nkki macc urd nkki » asggʷas n 2018, g tasiggzt n n ayt mllul, gant zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, d tamdrawt d tmawast n tussna tamṛṛukit.
* Ungal « Aɣyul d uzgn » iffaɣd asggʷas n 2018, g tasiggzt n n ayt mllul, gant zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, d tamdrawt d usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt.
* Ungal « Taɣufi issnfd ubayyuṛ » asggʷas n 2020, g tasiggzt n n ayt mllul, iga zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt.
* Adlis n ufran  « Taskla tamaziɣt tamaynut g lmṛṛuk :talalit »  g tasiggzt n n ayt mllul, iga zɣ tẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, d tmdrawt d usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt.

